Language Names

Have you ever wondered what the Spanish word for "Greek" is? Or maybe the Italian word for "Japanese"? The Finnish word for "Finnish"? If so, this page is for you.

Built using the Intl API that's built into Node.js versions 14+. Check out the source at github.com/zeke/language-names.
